  "texts": [
    "We trained the CNN-RNN model on the data from 1980 to 2016 and used 2017 data to do feature selection.",
    "Finally, we evaluated the performance of feature selection method on the 2018 yield prediction.",
    "We sorted all the features based on their estimated effects and selected the 50% and 75% most important features.",
    "Table 4 shows the yield prediction performance of the CNN-RNN model using these selected features.",
    "The prediction accuracy of the CNN-RNN model did not drop significantly compared to the CNN-RNN model using all the features (100%), which suggested that the feature selection method can successfully find the important features."
  ],
